changes from 0.3 to 1.0
-----------------------

* use autotools
* move source to subdirectory
* GNUify project with files like NEWS (this one), ChangeLog, AUTHORS and
  INSTALL
* add compile-time option to change path to configuration file

changes from 0.2 to 0.3
-----------------------

* whitespace cleanup in code
* fully implement skipgroups for initgroups_dyn
* implement the dynamic resolver
* add support for a configuration file
* resolve full range of static AIDs

changes from 0.1 to 0.2
-----------------------

* use LGPLv3 for all files
* implement initgroups_dyn to resolve groups for a given user

initial release 0.1
-------------------

* implement setpwent, endpwent, getpwent, getpwnam, getpwuid for passwd
  database
* implement setgrend, endgrent, getgrent, getgrnam, getgrgid for group database
